"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 29, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lhq1719663764480.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lhq1719663764480.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lhq1719663764480.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rjq1665702781649\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rjq1665702781649___cos_255856\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the cosine of X.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__topic_d81224e1_d81225e1_d81226e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__p_d81227e1_d81228e1_d81229e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$cos</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__section_w3025ab1b7b5_w3026ab1b7_w3027ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__p_d81230e1_d81231e1_d81232e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vResult = $cos($pi() * RADIANS)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__topic_d53537e1_d53538e1_d53539e1_d53540e1_d53541e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1230481e83\">Parameters</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__p_d81236e1_d81237e1_d81238e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>—angle in radians.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__topic_d53542e1_d53543e1_d53544e1_d53545e1_d53546e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1230481e95\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__p_d81242e1_d81243e1_d81244e1\">Calculated cosine X .</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__p_d81245e1_d81246e1_d81247e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__topic_d53547e1_d53548e1_d53549e1_d53550e1_d53551e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1230481e111\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__p_d81251e1_d81252e1_d81253e1\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__section_omv_mky_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1230481e120\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$cos</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example returns the cosine of the given expression:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rjq1665702781649__pre_wlj_nky_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vResult = $cos($pi() * RADIANS)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vyi1719662027228.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$acos</a><p>Return the arc cosine of X.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421997\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7421997\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$cos Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the cosine of X. $cos ( X ) Example: vResult = $cos($pi() * RADIANS) Parameters X —angle in radians. Return Values Calculated cosine X . If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Use Allowed in all component types. Example: Using $cos The following example returns the cosine of the given expression: vResult = $cos($pi() * RADIANS) Copy Related Links $acos Return the arc cosine of X. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}